songs.name: Fresh Eyes
songs.author: Andy Grammar
songs.description: Originally learned when Olivia was going to Africa. I was sad because she still hadn't told her family that we were planning to live together.  Also wanted to sing to her. I was afraid and anxious because of work and her.  And eye surgery. So I thought it'd be funny to sing the song so I can say I can see her with new eyes.
